# WROMANCEL proxy — must come BEFORE the SPA catch-all below.
# Netlify processes _redirects before netlify.toml; first match wins.
#
# No self-redirect (that caused a redirect loop). The game page detects the
# /wromancel prefix at runtime and builds ABSOLUTE API paths, so it works with or
# without a trailing slash — we just proxy straight through.
#
# Rule 1: /wromancel (exact) -> the daily page on Railway.
/wromancel              https://wromacel-v2-production.up.railway.app/daily.html   200

# Rule 2: everything under /wromancel/ (the API, assets, etc.) proxies through.
/wromancel/*            https://wromacel-v2-production.up.railway.app/:splat        200

# SPA fallback for the podcast site's client-side routes.
/*                      /index.html                                                200
